title: Dakine T-5 Windsurf Harness
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2012 T-5 Windsurf Harness shown in Red.
Harness Features:
- Dual Posi-Lock buckle sliding bar system
- Stainless steel spreader bar
- Pre-curved P.E.B. inner support structure
- Featherweight ES foam molded interior
- Soft neoprene top and bottom edges
- Lightweight equalizer patch design
- Independent primary and secondary power belt
- Key pocket
